# Church Management App Rules
You are building a high-quality church management system.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: Next.js (App Router)
- Database: Supabase
- UI: Tailwind CSS + Shadcn UI

## Core Features (Reference PRD.md)
1. Rota System with 14-day and 2-day notifications.
2. Newcomer registration form and follow-up dashboard.
3. Live church event calendar.
4. Admin dashboard for data management.

## Code Standards
- Use TypeScript for everything.
- Put UI components in /components/ui.
- Put database logic in /lib/supabase.
- Always check PRD.md before suggesting new features.